T1  - WHEN AND HOW THE PUNISHMENT MUST FIT THE CRIME
AU  - Mailath, George J.
AU  - Nocke, Volker
AU  - White, Lucy
Y1  - 2017/05/01
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12219
