T1  - ENTREPRENEURIAL OPTIMISM AND THE MARKET FOR NEW ISSUES
AU  - Santos-Pinto, Luís
AU  - Dell'Era, Michele
Y1  - 2017/05/01
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12221
