T1  - ESTIMATING A DYNAMIC SPATIAL EQUILIBRIUM MODEL TO EVALUATE THE WELFARE IMPLICATIONS OF REGIONAL ADJUSTMENT PROCESSES: THE DECLINE OF THE RUST BELT
